  "description": "<p>The Downtown rolltable is designed to enable unprepared or improvising cyberpunk GMs to generate the immediate urban environment, quickly and easily.</p><p>Roll 3-4 times on this table to tell you the type of buildings your players have in their immediate area.</p><p>Then roll the same amount of D10s. The numbers shown on each die can be used in a couple of different ways; to determine the number of floors the building has, and to find if it has any notable features (optional).</p><p> If you want a bigger structure, just double the result of that dice.</p>",
